headline: Wolfe upgrades Medtronic as pulsed field ablation may jolt near term growth
summary: Investing.com -- Wolfe Research upgraded Medtronic plc to Peer Perform from Underperform saying that an expected ramp‑up of its Affera pulsed‑field ablation (PFA) system could add up to two percentage points to organic revenue and help the medical‑device maker exceed its own 5% growth target in fiscal 2026.
